<s> See the following option as described on the Tidy page: keep-time: bool  </s>
<s> If set to yes, Tidy won't alter the last modified time for files it writes back to.  </s>
<s> The default is yes.  </s>
<s> This allows you to tidy files without effecting which ones will be uploaded to the Web server when using a tool such as 'SiteCopy'.  </s>
<s> Note that this feature may not work on some platforms.  </s>
